# AWS EC2 Web Server

## Project Overview
Deployed a production-style web server using AWS EC2 and Nginx.

## Steps Performed
1. Launched EC2 instance (Ubuntu)
2. Connected using SSH (PuTTY)
3. Updated system packages
4. Installed and configured Nginx
5. Hosted custom HTML website

## Output
Website hosted successfully using EC2 public IP.

## Tools Used
- AWS EC2
- Linux (Ubuntu)
- Nginx

